{"tid":1876854,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"各位有幾多個月存貨?","createTime":"2020-02-12T16:15:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T17:03:36.000Z","uid":319858,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6880a504b9038398d09abdf7f8d704437e84109b","tid":1876854,"uid":319858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T16:15:58.000Z","msg":"有PFE的口罩得兩個月<br />\n<br />\n淨BFE的得半個月<br />\n<br />\n夾埋兩個半月啦<br />\n<br />\n全部都係呢兩個禮拜晨早排翻黎<br />\n<br />\n同埋今日狂奔一公里衝日本城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點知係淨BFE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前就話過埋呢兩個禮拜就無口罩賣<br />\n<br />\n會唔會日本台灣口罩遲D產能過剩瘋狂翻貨?<br />\n<br />\n華潤堂又成日翻唔等使ge口罩但仲要同其他人鬥痴線鬥早 班人起碼三點鐘開始排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人知點算好 你地多唔多貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想未雨綢繆<br />\n<br />\n你趁呢個禮拜撲埋佢啦就正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你夠貨啦睇定D先啦就負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打算說服阿媽開通網上信用卡買amazon口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72fb09b3670791fca22a9547a18b7080aaa61811","tid":1876854,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T16:18:15.000Z","msg":"夠半年以上 pfe"},{"pid":"1e8a27cfdfdd2537a992aaff906afef61735aa29","tid":1876854,"uid":179782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T16:20:05.000Z","msg":"1個月全家用<br />\n我住果度仲有確診個案<br />\n但又唔敢成日出去搶口罩"},{"pid":"5dbfc3f6ba916d67950f7629a0e6de36244e4a7b","tid":1876854,"uid":148244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T16:20:10.000Z","msg":"巴打不如報埋價<br />\n你總共用咗幾多錢買口罩貨？<br />\n利申：$39/50盒 (搶購潮之前買)<br />\n一個月後冇貨了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1422bfab7c